Linux::Pid version 0.03
=======================

Returns what Linux' C library thinks the PID and PPID are.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires Inline and Inline::C version 0.43 or higher.
ETOOLAZY to make a XS version.

